@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Sign In

start

note right
Steps:
1. User opens login page
2. User enters credentials
3. System validates credentials
4. If valid, system loads profile and creates session
5. System shows dashboard OR error message
end note

:Open Login Page;
:Enter Username and Password;
:Validate Credentials;

if (Credentials valid?) then (Yes)
  :Load User Profile;
  :Create Session;
  :Show Dashboard;
else (No)
  :Show Error Message;
  :Return to Login Page;
endif

stop
@enduml
